  spook-controller (Deployment)       │  │","│  │  Watches MacOSVM CRDs               │  │","│  │  Calls HTTP API on Mac nodes        │  │","│  └──────────┬──────────────┬────────────┘  │","└─────────────│──────────────│───────────────┘","              │ HTTP :8484   │ HTTP :8484","     ┌────────▼──────┐  ┌───▼───────────┐","     │  Mac Host 01  │  │  Mac Host 02  │","     │  spook serve  │  │  spook serve  │","     │  ┌────┐┌────┐ │  │  ┌────┐┌────┐ │","     │  │VM-1││VM-2│ │  │  │VM-3││VM-4│ │","     │  └────┘└────┘ │  │  └────┘└────┘ │","     └───────────────┘  └───────────────┘"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The controller runs on a Linux node in your cluster. Mac nodes","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"run "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"spook serve"},{"type":"text","text":" natively as a LaunchDaemon (not as a pod —"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Mac nodes can’t run OCI containers). Each Mac supports up to","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"2 concurrent VMs per Apple’s EULA Section 2B(iii)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Prerequisites","text":"Prerequisites","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A Kubernetes cluster (v1.26+) with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"kubectl"},{"type":"text","text":" access"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"One or more Apple Silicon Macs running ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"spook serve --host 0.0.0.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Helm v3 for installing the operator","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A base VM on each Mac (created with ","type":"text"},{"code":"spook create base --from-ipsw latest","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":")","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"text":"Quick Start","level":2,"anchor":"Quick-Start","type":"heading"},{"text":